👉 Kya karta hai:-
WorkflowCase ke saare variables (args) return karta hai.

🧠 3️⃣ 2️⃣ setVariable(WorkflowCase workflowCase, String name, Object value):-
👉 Kya karta hai:-
WorkflowCase me naya variable add / update karta hai.

